description.en-US: Roxie is a nurturing and calm mother, always attentive to her pups. She has a gentle nature that brings comfort and warmth to everyone around her.
Clifford is a proud and loving father, known for his intelligence and gentle demeanor. He has a joyful presence that lights up the room.
Daisy is cheerful and playful, always bringing energy and warmth wherever she goes. Her friendly demeanor makes her a joy to be around.
A gentle giant! Damion is calm and composed, known for his gentle and steady presence. He has a quiet confidence that puts everyone at ease.

Beauty always exudes grace and serenity. She has a nurturing spirit that brings peace and joy to everyone she encounters. Whether it's caring for her pups or simply being by your side, Beauty's gentle presence is a constant source of comfort and love
Luke is an AKC registered poodle with a great temperament and a happy demeanor, he is always happy to meet someone new. Luke thrives on being outside and getting lots of exercise.
Ollie is a very sweet natured boy, with a happy-go-lucky personality, always ready to receive some love and attention.
Holly has about the sweetest disposition you could ask for, soaking up every every ounce of attention she can get, and loves to roll over for belly scritches.
Starla is the sweetest mother! Gentle and demure, she loves to nuzzle up for pets and give affection. She had a gorgeous light English Cream coat.
A beautiful F1 Goldendoodle dam with a gentle and sweet disposition, Alexandra is a wonderful mother who loves to be around people and soaks up all the love she can get !
Storm is full of playful energy and is always ready for her next adventure, making her the perfect companion for a fun-loving family! Be sure to note her beautiful merle coat!
Sienna’s sweet and curious nature will bring joy to any home, as she’s always eager to explore and make new friends.
Starlight loves to snuggle and has a gentle personality that will warm your heart, perfect for those cozy moments together.
Sandy is a little ray of sunshine, always bringing cheer with her joyful spirit and love for life’s little moments.
Stella is a smart and curious pup who loves learning new things, and she’s sure to make a wonderful addition to any loving family.
Sawyer is a charming little fellow with a playful personality who’s always up for fun and games, bringing laughter wherever he goes.
Samson has a gentle soul and a heart full of love, making him the perfect pup for someone looking for a loyal and loving companion.
Scout is an adventurous spirit, always ready to explore the world around him and bring excitement to every day!
Tucker’s fun-loving and friendly nature will instantly win you over, making him the perfect playmate for any family!
Teddy is a sweet and gentle boy who’s always ready for a cuddle, bringing love and warmth into your home.
Thor’s adventurous spirit and playful energy make him the ideal companion for anyone who loves outdoor fun and excitement!
Twyla is a little sweetheart with a curious nature and a heart full of affection, perfect for bringing joy to your everyday life.
Trixie’s happy-go-lucky attitude and playful charm make her a delightful addition to any family, ready to spread happiness.
Tara is a loving and loyal pup with a gentle personality, eager to become your forever friend and brighten your days.
Playful and curious, Aria has a curly, apricot coat and loves to explore. She’s full of energy and brings joy wherever she goes!
Ava is a sweet and lovable girl with soft, golden curls. Ava is calm, affectionate, and always ready for a snuggle.
Ace is a playful and adventurous pup with soft, golden curls. He’s always up for fun and brings excitement to every moment.
This little beauty has a warm, honey-colored coat and a gentle personality. Amber is as cuddly as she is playful, making her the perfect family companion.
With his curly, apricot-colored coat and confident personality, Apollo is a natural leader. He’s friendly, smart, and loves to explore new places.
Archie is a sweet and cuddly little guy with a love for people. His soft, wavy coat and playful nature make him a perfect family companion.
Calm and gentle, Asher has a rich golden coat and an affectionate personality. He’s loyal and loves to be by your side, making him the ideal cuddle buddy.
Smart and confident, Athena is always leading the way on new adventures. With her wavy, golden coat and bright eyes, she’s both beautiful and brave.

description.en-US: Calm and graceful, Aurora has a soft, cream-colored coat and a peaceful nature. She loves to relax by your side and shower you with affection.
Axel is full of energy and charm, with a soft, curly coat in shades of apricot & cream. He loves playing outdoors and always brings a smile with his happy-go-lucky spirit.
